column16: Johnny Giavotella grounds into double play, third baseman Danny Worth to second baseman Ramon Santiago to first baseman Don Kelly.    Jeff Francoeur out at 2nd.
Mike Moustakas pops out to second baseman Ramon Santiago.
Jeff Francoeur singles on a line drive to left fielder Delmon Young.    Melky Cabrera scores.    Eric Hosmer to 2nd.
Eric Hosmer singles on a ground ball to right fielder Andy Dirks.    Melky Cabrera to 3rd.
Melky Cabrera doubles (42) on a fly ball to right fielder Andy Dirks.
Juan Pierre singles on a ground ball to center fielder Austin Jackson.
Paul Konerko grounds out, third baseman Wilson Betemit to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Alexei Ramirez flies out to left fielder Delmon Young.
Juan Pierre grounds out, second baseman Carlos Guillen to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Melky Cabrera flies out to left fielder Delmon Young.
Alex Gordon walks.    Alcides Escobar to 2nd.
Alcides Escobar singles on a ground ball to shortstop Jhonny Peralta.  Johnny Giavotella advances to 3rd, on throwing error by shortstop Jhonny Peralta.
Brayan Pena pops out to shortstop Jhonny Peralta.
Johnny Giavotella singles on a line drive to left fielder Delmon Young.    Jeff Francoeur scores.    Mike Moustakas scores.
